Atinys, please keep voting and streaming!! Mcountdown Pre-Voting started today (on mwave) and we are so close to 1st place!!
And DON'T FORGET that really soon, Idolchamp and Starplay voting will start. We are low on charts and digital sales, but I know we can help Ateez win If we all stream the M/V and Comeback Live Stages + VOTE 3 TIMES EVERYDAY.
Let's work together please. Let's make up for ateez not winning ROTY; let's show them we work hard to support them too! FIGHTING!!
